                            <summary>
                                <p>Fragment of a Gelasian sacramentary containing parts from the <quote>Missa tam vivorum quam defunctorum</quote>, <quote>Super oblata</quote>, <quote>Missa abbatis et congregationis sibi comissae</quote>, and<quote>Missa votiva communis viventium</quote>, as identified by <bibl>
